data.description: DO YOU LOVE TO ENTERTAIN?? Then this is the house for you.  3 Bedroom, 2 Bath house conveniently located close to town.  Beautifully landscaped 1/2 Acre completely fenced.  Newly remodeled, this house has it all.  Open floor plan ideal for entertaining.  8 Seat Bar, Gourmet Kitchen with Island, Real wood cabinets, granite tops, Double Oven, Gas Stove/Griddle, SS Appliances, Vegetable sink with disposal.  Master bedroom is over sized with double doors leading outside.  Master Shower has electronic control with Main shower head, Overhead shower head, 4 Body Sprays, Handheld shower head, and Steam Generator.  It is AWESOME.  2nd bedroom has walk in closet.  This house is minutes from grocery, restaurants, movies, and more.  Must see to appreciate.  Please call to schedule showing.  305-522-3326
